                                                                                    ('Kentucky Heat', '0821773682', 383, '9/1/2002', 201, 'Determined to make her racing stables the best in Kentucky, Nealy Coleman Diamond finds her life forever changed by the arrival of her ex-husband''s law partner, Hatch Littletree, who helps her reconcile with her estranged children and opens her heart to the possibilities of newfound love and passion, but an unexpected tragedy threatens to destroy everything Nealy holds dear. 125,000 first printing.', 4.99, 'http://images.amazon.com/images/P/0821773682.01.THUMBZZZ.jpg', 'http://images.amazon.com/images/P/0821773682.01.MZZZZZZZ.jpg', 'http://images.amazon.com/images/P/0821773682.01.LZZZZZZZ.jpg'),
