                                                                                    ('Oscar Wilde', '0394759842', 736, '11/5/1988', 180, 'Presents an in-depth study of the complex and tragic life of Oscar Wilde and a tribute to his inimitable wit and brilliant writings', 8.79, 'http://images.amazon.com/images/P/0394759842.01.THUMBZZZ.jpg', 'http://images.amazon.com/images/P/0394759842.01.MZZZZZZZ.jpg', 'http://images.amazon.com/images/P/0394759842.01.LZZZZZZZ.jpg'),
