                                                                                    ('The Beach', '0582435676', 112, '2/19/2001', 103, 'A rootless young Westerner believes he has stumbled upon paradise on a remote island off Thailand, a place known as "The Beach,"until he discovers the deadly underside of the island''s culture', 5.29, 'http://images.amazon.com/images/P/0582435676.01.THUMBZZZ.jpg', 'http://images.amazon.com/images/P/0582435676.01.MZZZZZZZ.jpg', 'http://images.amazon.com/images/P/0582435676.01.LZZZZZZZ.jpg'),
