                                                                                    ('A Walk in the Woods: Rediscovering America on the Appalachian Trail', '0767902521', 284, '5/4/1999', 34, 'Published on the seventy-fifth anniversary of the Appalachian Trail, a wry account by the author of The Lost Continent traces an adventurous trek past the trail''s natural pleasures, human eccentrics, and offbeat comforts. $150,000 first printing. Tour.', 8.79, 'http://images.amazon.com/images/P/0767902521.01.THUMBZZZ.jpg', 'http://images.amazon.com/images/P/0767902521.01.MZZZZZZZ.jpg', 'http://images.amazon.com/images/P/0767902521.01.LZZZZZZZ.jpg'),
