                                                                                    ('The Fall', '0679720227', 147, '5/7/1991', 180, 'A noble beauty and an errant knight engage in a sensual battle of wits against a backdrop of shiftng loyalties, betrayal, and intrigue where one false move can bring about their ruin. Original.', 5.29, 'http://images.amazon.com/images/P/0679720227.01.THUMBZZZ.jpg', 'http://images.amazon.com/images/P/0679720227.01.MZZZZZZZ.jpg', 'http://images.amazon.com/images/P/0679720227.01.LZZZZZZZ.jpg'),
