                                                                                    ('The Lost Years of Merlin', '0441010288', 304, '7/2/2002', 3, 'When Merlin, suffering from a case of severe amnesia, discovers his strange powers, he becomes determined to discover his identity and flees to Fincayra where he fulfills his destiny, saving Fincayra from certain destruction and claiming his birthright and true name. Reprint.', 4.99, 'http://images.amazon.com/images/P/0441010288.01.THUMBZZZ.jpg', 'http://images.amazon.com/images/P/0441010288.01.MZZZZZZZ.jpg', 'http://images.amazon.com/images/P/0441010288.01.LZZZZZZZ.jpg'),
