                                                                                    ('Burning The Map', '0373250215', 288, '10/25/2002', 145, 'Twenty-six-year-old Casey Evers, who has her life perfectly mapped out, joins her two best friends on an illuminating trip to Rome and Greece, where she unexpectedly embarks on a journey of self-discovery that causes her to question her life and her long-term relationship with her boyfriend John. Original.', 5.29, 'http://images.amazon.com/images/P/0373250215.01.THUMBZZZ.jpg', 'http://images.amazon.com/images/P/0373250215.01.MZZZZZZZ.jpg', 'http://images.amazon.com/images/P/0373250215.01.LZZZZZZZ.jpg'),
