                                                                                    ('Secret for a Nightingale', '0449212963', 396, '10/12/1987', 93, 'With the outbreak of the Crimean War, Susanna Pleydell journeys to the Middle East to work as a nurse with the legendary Florence Nightingale, but is haunted by a dark secret from her past', 5.29, 'http://images.amazon.com/images/P/0449212963.01.THUMBZZZ.jpg', 'http://images.amazon.com/images/P/0449212963.01.MZZZZZZZ.jpg', 'http://images.amazon.com/images/P/0449212963.01.LZZZZZZZ.jpg'),
